M||tx|---
M|Quic|tx|1. Run `/weekly-rv` on Friday afternoon (best time) or Monday morning
M|Quic|2. I|weekly plans, daily plans, PRDs, meeting notes, decisions, and launches from the past 7 days
M|Quic|tx|3. I will gn a focused rv comparing plan vs. actual, surfacing key wins, blockers, and learnings
M|Quic|tx|4. Output goes to `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/YYYY-WXX-weekly-rv.md`
M|Quic|tx|5. After the rv, I will suggest running `/weekly-plan` to plan nx week
M|Quic|tx|**Default output is focused (~150 lines max).** Say "full rv" if you want the expanded version w/ stakeholder pulse, task-level execution metrics, and pattern al.
M|Purp|tx|End-of-week synthesis reviewing what you accomplished, what you learned, and what needs attention. Feeds into nx week's planning and builds institutional memory.
M|Usag|it|`/weekly-rv` - rv current/past week
M|Usag|it|`/weekly-rv last-week` - rv previous week (if you forgot)
M|Usag|tx|---
