M|Outp|Befo|
M|Outp|- [ |** If a weekly plan existed, every planned priority is addressed w/ a status (complete, partial, not started) and a reason for any gap.
M|Outp|- [ |** Each learning includes what happened, why, and a concrete change for nx time. "Work harder" is not a learning.
M|Outp|- [ |** At least 3 draft priorities for nx week are suggested, grounded in this week's outcomes and st goals.
M|Outp|- [ |** Every unresolved blocker has a specific action and person to contact on Monday.
M|Outp|- [ |** If launches happened or metrics data exists, actual numbers are cited (not just "things went well").
M|Outp|- [ |** Default rv is ~150 lines. Full rv is longer but still organized w/ clear section headers. Do not gn a full rv unless the us asked for one.
M|Outp|- [ |** The rv includes at least one thing that did not go as planned, w/ root cause al. A rv w/ only wins is incomplete.